# Summary
The HubSpot (Cohort Sync) destination enables syncing Amplitude-built cohorts to HubSpot contact lists for targeting, supporting both Email and Contact ID as user identifiers, with options for one-time or scheduled syncs that track additions and removals since the last sync.

